<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.6.9">
<l>tañca mākiya tantai tāyoṭu tāṉu māyavai yallaṉā</l>
<l>yeñca lilama rarku lamutaṉ mūvar tammuḷḷu mātiyai</l>
<l>yañci nīrula kattuḷ ḷīrka ḷavaṉi vaṉeṉṟu kūḻēṉmi</l>
<l>ṉeñci ṉāṉiṉaip pāṉya vaṉava ṉāku nīḷkaṭal vaṇṇaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who, being himself as father and mother who are refuge, being not those,</l>
<l>is the first among the primeval Three in the family of flawless immortals,</l>
<l>you who are in the world, afraid, don’t doubt “that one, this one”.</l>
<l>Whichever one is thought about in the heart, that one becomes the one the colour of the long sea.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
